# .forceignore — controls what sf CLI tracks/deploys
#
# Agent metadata (.agent-meta.xml, .agentTopic-meta.xml, .agentScript) is
# supported for deployment in API v62+ but has limited source-tracking support
# in some CLI versions. If your sf CLI throws errors on agent metadata, uncomment
# the line below to exclude it and deploy agents manually via Setup > Agentforce Agents.
#
# **/agents/**
